## Validation

The following verification checks were successfully completed:

- Ubuntu Server installed successfully.
- The server booted without errors.
- Internet connectivity was verified.
- Package repositories were updated.
- Installed packages were upgraded.
- System information was verified.
- Network configuration was confirmed.
- Disk and memory resources were verified.

---

## Challenges Encountered

During the initial setup, the server was unable to resolve `google.com`, resulting in a **"Temporary failure in name resolution"** error. This issue was caused by a DNS configuration problem. After correcting the DNS configuration, internet connectivity was successfully restored and the server was able to resolve domain names correctly.

